{"legislative_session": "119", "identifier": "HCONRES 84", "title": "Directing the President pursuant to section 5(c) of the War Powers Resolution to remove United States Armed Forces from Lebanon.", "from_organization": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": ["resolution"], "subject": [], "abstracts": [], "other_titles": [], "other_identifiers": [{"identifier": "ocd-bill-us-119-hconres84"}], "actions": [{"description": "Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.", "date": "2026-06-04T20:43:55+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "On agreeing to the resolution Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 92 - 324, 2 Present (Roll no. 201).", "date": "2026-06-04T20:43:53+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Failed of passage/not agreed to in House On agreeing to the resolution Failed by the Yeas and Nays: 92 - 324, 2 Present (Roll no. 201).", "date": "2026-06-04T20:43:53+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered as unfinished business. (consideration: CR H3872)", "date": "2026-06-04T20:01:39+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "POSTPONED PROCEEDINGS - At the conclusion of debate on H. Con. Res. 84, the Chair put the question on agreeing to the concurrent resolution and by voice vote, announced the noes had prevailed. Ms. Tlaib demanded the yeas and nays and the Chair postponed further proceedings until a time to be announced.", "date": "2026-06-03T23:47:22+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "The previous question was ordered pursuant to a previous order of the House.", "date": "2026-06-03T23:47:16+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "DEBATE - The House resumed debate on H. Con. Res. 84.", "date": "2026-06-03T23:09:53+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "WORDS TAKEN DOWN - During the course of debate, exception was taken to certain words used and a demand was made to have the words taken down. After review, the Chair ruled that the words were in violation of the spirit of debate. Without objection, the words were stricken from the record.", "date": "2026-06-03T23:09:30+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "DEBATE - The House proceeded with one hour of debate on H. Con. Res. 84.", "date": "2026-06-03T21:36:00+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Considered pursuant to a previous order. (consideration: CR H3814-3822; text: CR H3814)", "date": "2026-06-03T21:35:56+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "Consideration initiated pursuant to a previous order.", "date": "2026-06-03T21:35:30+00:00", "organization_id": "~{\"classification\": \"lower\"}", "classification": [], "related_entities": []}, {"description": "ORDER OF PROCEDURE - Mr. Mast asked unanimous consent that, it be in order at any time to consider H. Con. Res. 84 in the House if called up by the chair of the Committee on Foreign Affairs or his designee; that the concurrent resolution be considered as read; and that the previous question be considered as ordered on the concurrent resolution to adoption without intervening motion except for one hour of debate equally divided and controlled by Representative Mast of Florida and Representative Tlaib of Michigan, or t